{"tid":630574,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺摩狗好撚重心計 xx(","createTime":"2018-04-15T16:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T18:10:37.000Z","uid":33058,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2794234c3a949f7119096d75e8ffad6c284004b9","tid":630574,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 摩狗又搞串鏝個party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知英超鏝實拎硬<br />\n搞到人地唔係嬴波奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時鏝乜都野mood都唔夠而家呢下高<br />\n<br />\n第2，下場西布朗對痢，又幫西布朗打起隊波黎撚利狗<br />\n<br />\n第3，盡量幫西布朗護級 比左保貴3分，下季又多隻私家雞用<br />\n<br />\n第4，幫英超增加護級競爭性同觀賞性，未到最後一刻都唔知邊隊降<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獌狗輸比榜尾 而家唔笑 唔通拜山先笑咩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b565d6f55d50a8f8960b179ede64f64de43597","tid":630574,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1734875cde15f0a82e93fe0e00a4e370b0d257","tid":630574,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eec54416a2646428fe2fbedf656f5f94f7e8a1","tid":630574,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaf03904dc8ec2113e3a2b374297d1cd940f33b","tid":630574,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c